      "role": "user",
      "content": "but its not like a normal appliance sound. its more like... rhythmic. and it only happens when they are home or when i'm alone in the house. i tried moving to the bedroom and it felt slightly different but the anxiety stayed. it's like the vibration is specifically tuned to mess with my head. have you heard of people using infrasound or low frequency stuff for this kind of thing? i looked it up and it seems possible.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
